      },
      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role (A72/A73):</strong> the Red Mantis <strong>guild-mistress</strong> from Mediogalti Island — Cinnabar's former commander — who took charge of the eight assassins who survived the Deathhead Vault rout. Ileosa gave them the fourth floor; Kayltanya has <strong>forbidden revenge on the PCs</strong> until the queen returns from her 'errand' and funds reinforcements — the PCs' arrival in the castle voids that order. She sleeps in the bar's hammock (A73) and joins the A72 hammock-ambush the moment it erupts. The Crown's last professional.</p>",
      "publication": {
        "title": "Pathfinder: Curse of the Crimson Throne (PF2e conversion, private)",
